item.title: I need 10 mins of 1 of ur time plssss
item.dc:creator: @Mendorphins Mendorphins
item.description:
@Mendorphins wrote:

Your mates play your server, not your client. Make sure you set up a No-IP and have the IP you set-up, set in your client.java before releasing the client to your friends.

You can use the search bar to find a tutorial if you’re not sure where/how, as you haven’t gave us much information about your client (and every client is different).

Go to: http://www.canyouseeme.org/ to see if your IP and ports are being blocked. If they are, make an exception in your firewall/antivirus or disable them completely.
